snippet.title: Against the Storm - 1.0 Release Date Announcement | Coming to PC Game Pass
snippet.description:
Rebuild civilization in the face of apocalyptic rains!
▶ https://store.steampowered.com/app/1336490/Against_the_Storm/

Against the Storm is leaving Early Access and the 1.0 version is coming to Steam, GOG, Epic Games Store, and PC Game Pass on December 8, 2023!

As the Queen’s Viceroy, lead humans, beavers, lizards, foxes, and harpies to reclaim the wilderness and secure a future for civilization's last survivors.
